OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy low cloud possible
OL,6,Falong the coast, breaking up through
OL,7,Fthe morning to leave a dry day with
OL,8,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling cooler
OL,9,Fthan recent days in the onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry, but with patchy
OL,12,Flow cloud spreading inland from the
OL,13,Fcoast. Some showers possible in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of Thursday, perhaps heavy
OL,15,Fat times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAny low cloud quickly
OL,18,Fclearing to leave a fine day, with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunshine and temperatures
OL,20,Fincreasing again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
